- memory usage improved;
- fixed some bugs;

data.description:
Simple watchface with big solid digits.

Big Digits features:
- current time with seconds;
- AM/PM icon for 12-hour format;
- current week day;
- auto or manual color mode (via settings page);
- vibrates on Bluetooth connection lost (optional);
- Bluetooth status;
- battery level.

Next milestone:
- show date;

For any feedback, please mail me via link below!
Thank you! :)
